data.description: Gorgeous Rock Creek Village 2 bedroom, 2 full bath condo. Lofted master bedroom suite with new carpet and lots of light from 4 skylights.~ The unit boasts refinished hardwood floors and a fresh coat of paint throughout. The kitchen has been updated with granite counter tops and a breakfast bar. The bathrooms have been updated as well. Lots of storage and washer/dryer in unit. Walking distance to Rock Creek Park, Rock Creek Shopping Center, and Silver Spring Metro 0.5 mile away. All utilities included in Condo fee. Community has picnic/grilling patio, playground, and bike room. Square footage does not include the loft. Owner is a licensed Real Estate Agent in Maryland.
